Describe the bug
 When a code is built from source, there are tones of warning messages.
 <denchmark-code>warning: unknown warning option '-Wno-expansion-to-defined'; did you mean '-Wno-macro-redefined'?
       [-Wunknown-warning-option]
 </denchmark-code>
 
 To Reproduce
 Build from source using current master branch
 Desktop (please complete the following information):
 
 OS: OSX (10.12.6)
 
 Additional context
 Need to fix CmakeList.txt
